# Rust formatting (CI)

GitHub Actions runs `cargo fmt --all --check` (and fails the job if the tree is not formatted).

**After editing any `*.rs` file**, run:

```sh
cargo fmt --all
```

Before pushing or marking Rust work complete, verify:

```sh
cargo fmt --all --check
```

exits with status 0. This is separate from tests (`cargo test` is still avoided per project rules when tests are slow); `rustfmt` is fast and required for CI green.
